[private api] Contains MobilitySession implementation classes.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
MobilitySessionInternal Internal interface used by the library, extends the public MobilitySession interface with methods for processing incoming requests, as required by the library.
 

Class Summary
MobilityContextInternal A "back-end" implementation of MobilityContext with package-private setter methods to allow MobilitySession (in this same pacakge) to set thread-local values while keeping the setters methods non-public.
